def axiom : Sort -> Sort.
[]  axiom prop     --> type z
[i] axiom (type i) --> type (s i).
(; Coqine axiom = axiom ;)

[x] Axiom x (axiom x) --> true.

def rule : Sort -> Sort -> Sort.
[s  ] rule prop     s        --> s
[   ] rule _        prop     --> prop
[i,j] rule (type i) (type j) --> type (max i j).
(; Coqine rule = rule ;)

[s1,s2] Rule s1 s2 (rule s1 s2) --> true.



